track_notes: There are multiple tracks that will get you from parking to the summit, but this one has the least extreme incline.

Sometimes the road is open to vehicles, sometimes it is not.  When not open to vehicles, it is a very nice hike.  Alltrails lists a route that is partially on the PCT.  I took the service road all the way.  Not as scenic but more direct.  Nice campground at the top.

Completed May 27, 2023
